This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with the evaluation of dialogue response generation systems. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as these fields are closely related to dialogue systems. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as the paper discusses the use of metrics to evaluate dialogue systems. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.SD (Software Engineering) as the paper provides recommendations for future development of better automatic evaluation metrics for dialogue systems.
